			<description>You can consider this field like the <html:b>Code tab</html:b> of a Custom Button. The only difference is that the code in this field is triggered by a &quot;click&quot; <html:b>event</html:b>, while the code in a <html:b>Code tab</html:b> of a Custom Button is triggered by a &quot;command&quot; <html:b>event</html:b>.</description>
			<description>Additionally, all variables/objects that are available on the execution context of any button, like <html:b>self</html:b>, <html:b>Cc</html:b>, <html:b>Ci</html:b>, etc, are also available on the execution context of the code defined on this field.</description>
